Biography

Fayetteville State

-Third season playing at FSU following transfer from Louisburg College

-2023-24 (Senior): Scored a season-high 27 at Augusta on 12/2/23....Tied a season-high mark with 27 points on 1/6/24 vs. Lincoln....named HBCU National Player of the Week on...named CIAA Week 8 Defensive Player of the Week

-2022-23 (Junior): Played in 26 games (25 starts), leading the team in minutes per game (29.3), points per game (12.6), assists (52) and steals (66)....hit the game-winning shot at the buzzer to defeat Johnson C. Smith 60-59 on 2/4/23

-2021-22 (Sophomore): Averaged 13.0 points per game, 3.6 rebounds per game and totalled 70 steals in first season with FSU

-Attended Havelock High School in Havelock, North Carolina
